versions

nexus

java-library    adds dependency (inject)
license         versions, java-library (soft)
groovy          versions, java-library (soft), adds dependency (groovy)
groovydoc       versions, groovy (soft)
logging         adds dependencies (slf4j, logback(test))
spock           adds dependencies (groovy (test), spock(test))

cobertura       no deps but recommended to apply after java/groovy plugins
